001package org.biopax.ols.impl;
002
003import org.biopax.ols.DbXref;
004
005import java.io.Serializable;
006
007public class DbXrefBean implements DbXref, Serializable {
008
009    private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;
010
011    private String parentObjectPk;
012    private long dbXrefId;
013    private String dbName = null;
014    private String accession = null;
015    private String description = null;
016    private int xrefType;
017
018    public long getDbXrefId() {
019        return dbXrefId;
020    }
021
022    public void setDbXrefId(final long _dbXrefId) {
023        dbXrefId = _dbXrefId;
024    }
025
026    public String getDbName() {
027        return dbName;
028    }
029
030    public void setDbName(final String _dbName) {
031        dbName = _dbName;
032    }
033
034    public String getAccession() {
035        return accession;
036    }
037
038    public void setAccession(final String _accession) {
039        accession = _accession;
040    }
041
042    public int getXrefType() {
043        return xrefType;
044    }
045
046    public void setXrefType(final int _version) {
047        xrefType = _version;
048    }
049
050    public String getDescription() {
051        return description;
052    }
053
054    public void setDescription(String description) {
055        this.description = description;
056    }
057
058    public String getParentObjectPk() {
059        return parentObjectPk;
060    }
061
062    public void setParentObjectPk(String parentObjectPk) {
063        this.parentObjectPk = parentObjectPk;
064    }
065
066    public String toString() {
067        return "DbName: " + dbName + " Acc: " + accession + " type: " + xrefType;
068    }
069
070    @Override
071    public boolean equals(Object o) {
072        if (o instanceof DbXrefBean) {
073            if (o != null) {
074                DbXrefBean dx = (DbXrefBean) o;
075                if (xorNull(dbName, dx.getDbName()) ||
076                        xorNull(accession, dx.getAccession())) {
077                    return false;
078                } else {
079                    boolean retval = true;
080
081                    //if still here, dbName is either null or not null in both DbXrefBeans
082                    //if not null, compare for equality
083                    if (dbName != null)
084                        retval = retval && dbName.equals(dx.getDbName());
085
086                    //same for dbXrefs
087                    if (accession != null)
088                        retval = retval && accession.equals(dx.getAccession());
089
090                    return retval;
091                }
092            } else {
093                return false;
094            }
095        } else {
096            return false;
097        }
098    }
099
100    private boolean xorNull(Object a, Object b) {
101        return (a == null) ? (b != null) : (b == null) ;
102    }
103}
